Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天在后山好像发生了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀 好像出现了别国的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警卫部队打倒了其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且回收了尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今天别让学生们靠近后山比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许还留有残党呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿平安无事才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体呢 尸体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然经常在这附近晃悠比较熟悉 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该问一下他们详细的地点来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干吗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上回学校去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里依旧有危险分子存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受人所托 怎么能半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是你的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥只有这种时候才摆出一副老师的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师根本不理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我回学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是被同伴疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不关心我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这次不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我将战利品带回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就会认同我这个伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就不再是孤单一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想体会那种感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我一定要将战利品带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不能让你留在这座危险的后山里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 我的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀 色诱术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人还真是单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…战斗过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 在这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真头痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天什么都没吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么可吃的东西呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种形状我从没见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是昨天战斗时 敌方忍者用的苦无了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来 我找到战利品了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把苦无
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们要寻找的密函吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在被打倒之前 他把苦无藏在了鸟窝里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大功告成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是个麻烦的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便应付一下他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子…就这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对他一点也不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母双亡后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也没有人夸奖我 认可我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在班上 我经常干蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我希望被人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟当时的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以借我点钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 你把零花钱全花在零食上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了零食 我还能花在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借你一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还在上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跟陌生人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则老爸会跟我发火的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈良鹿丸和秋道丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道我们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是鹿角和丁座的儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得真像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把你们翘课的事告诉他们好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天改自习课了 是吧 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人去后山找尸体了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡老师随后就去找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡老师去找鸣人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 自习不代表下课了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快回学校去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我也有同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖将那把苦无交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这个我绝对不会给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 看来我们得动粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色诱术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾 这个术可不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直就是犯规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 分身术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次见到这么不中用的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍术如果不管用的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对这座森林里布置的陷阱可是了如指掌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 怎么能被这种不入流的陷阱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小兔崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个陷阱在哪儿来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清醒点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了 一起回学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些外人在木叶鬼鬼祟祟地想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老老实实地把那个小鬼交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾这个傻瓜学生很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此你也要小命不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越傻越可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且我也不是那么容易被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 包围他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会保护好鸣人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑 散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影多重手里剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你的学生那听到了一些消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增援来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起收拾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁连携术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走 伊鲁卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迦楼罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是卡卡西先生及时赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅凭我一人 怕是难以脱险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有你一个 也能保护好鸣人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我似乎有些明白卡卡西先生的那番话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未直面过鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是在不断地回避着他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今后我一定会直面鸣人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…木叶村的警卫部署
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是她们潜入的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽快调整村里的警备部署
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说事出偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这次鸣人的莽撞反而拯救了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:14:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您让我成为了鸣人的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因此我才会想起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经我决定做一名老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为您那时对我的一番教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经一年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将悲伤压抑在笑容之下 很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你班主任那儿听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在学校里总是大家开心的焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…才没有悲伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者死于任务是一种荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲也好 母亲也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是用性命从妖狐手中保卫了村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我则是英雄之子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会孤单 不会难过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是喜悦之泪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你总是孤单一人抱膝而坐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶村的忍者们都拥有火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想要保卫这个村子的强烈愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是拥有这个意志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的大伙们都是他的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡 你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想将第三代的火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:16:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传给后人 传给鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 为啥将我辛苦找回的战利品给弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 你差点丢了小命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎么这么听话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让我第一次看到伊鲁卡老师发这么大火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师决定以后要好好关注你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 从明天起会严格调教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愈发不想去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你拥有火之意志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志 那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想要保护这个村子的强烈愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你拥有它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能变得如火影大人般的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影真的那么厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不只是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影大人还深受村民们的敬仰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是引领我们的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是从妖狐手中保护了村子的英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为比第四代更厉害的火影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后用我的力量得到大家的认同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你长这么高的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就能当上火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会拼命努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要成功给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没准真能成为火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊鲁卡老师 过来帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我这就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水月去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两三天前出去后就没回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好别回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都听到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩首大刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还惦记着它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就怪你当时没带上它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我找得好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和八尾那种怪物交战时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁还有空管这种累赘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把半死不活的你们扛回来的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别内讧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真以恩人自居了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他呢 反正也找回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了它果然缺乏斗志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下人都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤势痊愈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面前往木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到佩因会战败
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大跌眼镜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小南也不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 一下子少了这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要一个能和外道魔像同步的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼鲛 你去找八尾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有其他事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会这么惨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是佩因所为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过鸣人已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打倒了佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人他…那九尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他凭借自己的力量压制了九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人自己将九尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可没工夫让你吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来重建村子可不轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我们需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召开紧急会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上忍班长鹿角先生 请立刻前往大名殿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是鸣人的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个傻小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.95,0:22:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你来负责教导最为合适
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外宇智波佐助也在你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会那么简单就心慈手软的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指导上忍 旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来相当棘手啊
